WEBVTT

1
01:09:08.560 --> 01:09:11.350 
不，你前面说了她就站在那里
No, you said before that she was sitting back there... Standing back there...

2
01:09:11.430 --> 01:09:13.900 
对，就在我的客厅里
Yes, back in my parlour there.

3
01:09:13.980 --> 01:09:16.110 
她很饿，我为她做了份三明治
She was very hungry and I made her a sandwich

4
01:09:16.190 --> 01:09:21.610 
然后她说她累了，就直接去睡觉了
and then she said that she was tired and she had to go right to bed.

5
01:09:21.690 --> 01:09:23.860 
她怎么付钱的？
I see. How did she pay you?

6
01:09:23.950 --> 01:09:25.280 
- 现金还是支票？ - 现金
- Cash? Cheque?  - Cash.

7
01:09:25.370 --> 01:09:26.700 
现金
Cash, huh?

8
01:09:27.780 --> 01:09:31.450 
- 她离开后，没有再回来？ - 为什么会再来？
- And after she left, she didn't come back?  - Well, why should she?

9
01:09:31.540 --> 01:09:32.540 
对
Yeah.

10
01:09:37.170 --> 01:09:40.250 
阿伯盖斯先生，我想这就是全部了
Well, Mr Arbogast, I guess that's about it.

